29/04/2003
TIRANA, Albania -- On Monday (28 April), Defence Minister Pandeli Majko left for Prague, at the invitation of his Czech counterpart, Jaroslav Tvrdik. 
The talks will focus on mutual co-operation in the defence and security area and related future projects. 
Majko will also visit the Military Equipment Fair in Brno, one of the largest such fairs in Europe. 
(ATA - 28/04/03)
